summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to licensing and regulation of taxicabs and for-hire vehicles adding Chapters 5 and 6 to the New Seattle License Code, (Ordinance 108934) repealing Section 400--413, 500-508, 510--514, 520--526 of the License Code (Ordinance 49022) and repealing Ordinance 97389 as amending, relating to licensing and regulation of Cabulances.
